query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `smsProviderConfig` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `provider` enum('twilio','aws_sns','custom') NOT NULL,
  `accountSid` varchar(255),
  `authToken` text,
  `fromPhoneNumber` varchar(50),
  `awsAccessKeyId` varchar(255),
  `awsSecretAccessKey` text,
  `awsRegion` varchar(50),
  `customApiUrl` text,
  `customApiKey` text,
  `isActive` tinyint DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `dailyLimit` int DEFAULT 1000,
  `monthlyLimit` int DEFAULT 10000,
  `costPerSms` bigint DEFAULT 0,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `smsProviderConfig_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
)
